{"tid":1540671,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"極危險!!!這一步，林鄭已佔上風","createTime":"2019-09-04T12:08:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T12:18:20.000Z","uid":315857,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1178b5bae8c386cc181f17e4083ea069ba6eb1c5","tid":1540671,"uid":315857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T12:08:59.000Z","msg":"<ins><span style=\"color: red;\">原因我唔再重復，呢位師兄已經寫得好好：</span></ins><br />\n[六大陰謀］林鄭宣布撤回反送中的陰謀 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1539227\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1539227</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>作爲弱者將指控和黑警行動合理化</ins></span><br />\n重點係，林鄭同政府一直將自己包裝成弱者，宜家加埋呢招，政府同黑警對示威者既指控同埋會被合理化，更加容易得寸進尺。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>抗爭戰術必須立刻調整</ins></span><br />\n宜家最危險既事，就是沿用一直既抗爭方式，不作任何思考同埋行動上既改善，感性行動，咁好容易俾佢地得寸進尺。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><ins><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">所以宜家要贏既方法如下</span></ins></span><br />\n我都唔知有咩方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌你，你以爲我好有智慧啊.... <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之所以我地要大家一齊諗啊，仆街!!!<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n贏到呢場抗爭既方法點會一篇文章搞點<br />\n不過小第覺得以下幾點可以參考:<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><ins><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">1. 必須用計<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></ins></span><br />\n林鄭同政府一直以來都係生硬同冇想像力，但我地唔可以係咁!!! 冷氣軍師，和理非同埋前線返左屋企都要上連登參與思考同檢討，目標係阻止林鄭繼續將自己包裝成弱者。係咁既政權下，人民先係真正既弱者，呢點必須強化同埋體現出嚟。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><ins><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">2. 不戰而屈人之兵，用婉轉戰術<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></ins></span><br />\n孫子兵法入面既最高目標。不過，就算要戰鬥，都要用敵人屌唔到自己既戰術。好似之前係機場同大陸人影相扮中港一家親（綁完大陸人之後個一日）個種戰術。唔係話要走去機場做番呢啲野，而係係線要盡量用呢種郁完人，人地都屌唔到你既戰術，否則只會俾林鄭將佢嘅行動合理化，同埋抹黑我地。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><ins><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">3. 唔好被仇恨支配<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></ins></span><br />\n係梁天琦俾我地其中一個最寶貴既建議。但係我想講唔係剩係仇恨，而係包括所有會影響判斷既情感，例如階段性勝利既興奮，定係睇到西方媒體支持就係到自high。<br />\n如果你捉過棋你一定明白當捉到某個水平既時候，雙方所鬥既其中一樣係冷靜。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><ins><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">4. 保留前線力量<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></ins></span><br />\n我唔肯定，但係真心覺得班狗會更加猖狂打人同埋拉人，如果前線繼續勇武落去，會損耗前線力量同士氣。強烈建議立刻將抗爭暫時變成和理非，保留前線力量，就算要用勇武，都必須用更加多時間思考婉轉戰術，要可以避免前線流失既戰術，避免直接沖，多啲和理非集會。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><ins><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">5. 加強其他戰線<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></ins></span><br />\n現在對情況對前線勇武越來越不利，所以建議避免直接沖，反而要加強其他抗爭方式，尤其係文宣，同埋西方媒體同政權支持，罷工罷課，抵制中資，等等....<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><ins><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">6. 不割席、不分化、不篤灰<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></ins></span><br />\n亦都要嘗試獲得中間派既支持，務求好似200萬+1人上街個種團結和氣勢，呢種人數既活動基本上係令林鄭出唔到聲被噤住，剩係可以做錄音機。有番呢種氣勢既時候佢想點樣扮弱者都唔得。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: large;\">小弟P牌仔求大家唔好屌我</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><ins><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">最緊要係大家一定要一齊諗計!!!!</span></ins></span>"},{"pid":"71b02347d6ae4a1e48cb494cb1fca80f69cd1302","tid":1540671,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T12:15:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">撤LLM 對準政權</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3E7OjKb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3E7OjKb.gif&h=66b4ea40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zNutjAi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzNutjAi.jpg&h=1817afe5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">得到黨媒認證</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sELTeyX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsELTeyX.png&h=0e8c0efe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">#Chinazi旗係一個符號，不斷向世界輸出反共思想！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">#Chinazi 赤納粹</span></span></strong><br />\nChinazi就係China+Nazi。<br />\n赤=共產紅色恐怖, 納粹不解釋。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"> 全民反共 對準政權！</span></span></strong><br />\n黑警、黨鐵，港共全部都係人民既敵人<br />\n而背後一直有一個終極大Boss中共<br />\n<br />\n呢一刻中共絕對係十個煲得兩個蓋，準備爆煲。<br />\n今日唔號召世界圍堵中共，更待何時？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">用#Chinazi黎connect全世界</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">1. Connect所有黃絲。</span></strong><br />\n殘酷既現實係，並唔係所有黃絲都支持勇武。但黃絲最驚就係共產黨打到黎，一於用反共connect呢班淺黃!<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">2. Connect部分中立/藍絲。</span></strong><br />\n中立/藍絲既上一輩，全部都係親身經歷過六四既年代，唔少甚至係大陸生活過。係大陸生活上所面對既不公義、中共點砌人生豬肉、佢地可能比我地感受更深。佢地唔會否認對共產黨既恐懼！一齊黎喚醒佢地對中共既不信任！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">3. Connect全世界</span></strong><br />\nNazi既惡行到今時今日都依然係全世界既傷口，但佢地未必注意到係21世紀有個同Nazi不遑多讓既Chinazi！用#chinazi旗加海量文宣，話比佢地知我地既共同敵人係中共！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>目標：全香港市民都知到呢個符號！<br />\n請大家用各種創意方法令大家知道呢道Chinazi旗！<br />\n記住！存在即勝利！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">雙手奉上</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/09/02/9dojRG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F09%2F02%2F9dojRG.png&h=baf47345&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JXMrzU3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJXMrzU3.jpg&h=4fd76574&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uZFWW8o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuZFWW8o.jpg&h=4196affc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"86f456df640377346e01b57316d9d22d131b9894","tid":1540671,"uid":235374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T12:16:51.000Z","msg":"敵疲我打，敵退我追!!"},{"pid":"ebdae3e558777e8428fc859f3c600d2790762e46","tid":1540671,"uid":275634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T12:18:20.000Z","msg":"緩兵之計，借機清算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n將個波踢比立法會奶共派，即係否決撤回<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}